data.description: This exquisite and beautifully appointed home is tastefully converted into 2 separately metered units. There is also an additional 3rd basement unit. All three units have private entrances and full kitchen. Beautifully land scaped with patio, deck & privacy fence. Two car garage with several addition off street parking spots. Perfect for living in one unit and with rent from the other two units to pay the mortgage.
